  Comprehensive Architecture Report: Cybernetics Agent — Data Processing & Prompt/Context Control

  1. High-Level Architecture

  The agent is a Python orchestrator built around a single AIAgent class (run_agent.py:320) that runs an iterative tool-calling loop. The agent has been heavily refactored: AIAgent is a thin shell, with all real logic
  delegated to the agent/ package (~75 modules, ~2.3M LOC including adapters/helpers). Key subsystems:

